# ─── Prompt backup (copy/paste if automation fails) ──────────────────────────
#
# SETUP
#   Delete all files from this library.
#
# DEMO — Part 1: File rename skill
#   Our company policy is to name files [company,customer,product file is about]-[MM_DD_YYYY]-[1-word-what-is-this].[extension]. Make a skill to properly name files using the creation date of the document.
#
#   Update the file-rename skill to use camel case for the 1-word descriptor.
#
#   Review the files here to make sure they align to the company policy.
#
# DEMO — Part 2: YouTube description
#   Generate a youtube description for this file.
#
# DEMO — Part 3: Color palette skill
#   Read this color palette. Tell me about the color palette it recommends.
#
#   Create a skill that ensures anything we style uses this color palette.
#
#   Make this view pretty.
#
# RESET
#   Delete any skill related to file naming or renaming, if one exists.
#
#   Delete any skill related to color palette or styling, if one exists.
#
#   Delete all files from this library.
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
